{"tid":689587,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Chef Lemon又有新嘢　天然無添加拌麵有幾掂","createTime":"2018-06-04T07:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T09:12:13.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed7536aa16e6937cc386e7f43b7ea533f801eda","tid":689587,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"【特約報道】由謝霆鋒親自監製的鋒味拌麵，在台灣開賣時掀起了搶購熱潮，現在不用飛去台灣入貨，因為3款口味的「鋒味拌麵」已經抵港，包括麻辣、櫻花蝦紅油及三杯。每盒獨立包裝的拌麵（$25/盒)，視乎不同口味分別加入醬料及調味料。謝霆鋒用了足足一年時間，才研製出完全沒有加防腐劑、香料、色素及味精的無添加乾拌麵。麵條用上優質進口麵粉及無人工添加物，加上非油炸方法製成麵條，是百分百純天然的健康拌麵。醬料則以非基因改造黃豆釀製而成的醬油調配而成，成本比一般醬油高，但更加健康美味。 <br />\n要品嘗到拌麵的最佳滋味，不妨參照以下的煮食方法。首先將麵條放入滾水中，邊煮邊輕輕攪散麵條，約3.5分鐘後撈起並瀝乾水分，加入醬料及調味料拌勻即成。 <br />\n此外，大家亦可視乎個人喜好，加入鋒味出品的櫻花蝦XO醬或鮑魚等配料，令拌麵口感與味道更加豐富。「鋒味拌麵」的售賣點除中環鋒味旗艦店外，亦可在高級超市及大型商場開設的期間限定Pop Up銷售店選購，當中包括銅鑼灣崇光（即日至6月19日）、沙田一田超市（即日至6月13日）、尖沙咀美麗華商場（即日至9月4日）等。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180603/mobile/bkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180603%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001.html&d=gqSN%2BKN5GisA85iYsxYcARFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=43229d78\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180603/mobile/bkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ac07839d61c802be689c4158fce47077bd172f6","tid":689587,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"即場試食的Amanda表示，3款味道都好好食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001_06p.jpg?20180603141845\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001_06p.jpg%3F20180603141845&h=8a385ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEddie及Kelly就覺得味道天然無添加，吃完不覺口渴。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001_07p.jpg?20180603141845\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001_07p.jpg%3F20180603141845&h=0b1d39cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經常以即食麵醫肚的Tony就大讚麵條夠彈牙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20180603/photo/bkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001_08p.jpg?20180603141845\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20180603%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180603120004729-0603_00982_001_08p.jpg%3F20180603141845&h=e8083205&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69be51be07ae5b643160607021f0a2554abcb91d","tid":689587,"uid":44267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"Amanda<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba671d1fc97f3670acb44e29702ad57d4968e620","tid":689587,"uid":135896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"啲試食全部好淡定，對答好自然，一睇就知專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711becfa53c3cfaf62b15c6662463d6bb44c2cd9","tid":689587,"uid":43070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:12:13.000Z","msg":"假到咁，肯定係逆向思維，等你地笑鳩佢假搏收宣傳之效，垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}